metadata.name: Collide
metadata.description:
The sea of heaven is a place of wondrous colliding thoughts, of light and starry night skies that stretch on endlessly. 
Where the light of a thousand stars twinkle against the deep cobalt depths and the infinite universe unveils its beauty. 
Taking in a sky so vast is a reminder that even our most battered thoughts can float away and be free.

Artwork by Loechii
